{"tid":1700762,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"逼近真相：新證據指向周梓樂「突然」重返停車場、港人痛失科大高材生、何君堯到底是否自編自導？《政解．悶透社．王陽翎","createTime":"2019-11-08T16:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T16:23:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"905a7aa6facb5b09de325436278c4a88d6be1f01","tid":1700762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"逼近真相：新證據指向周梓樂「突然」重返停車場、<br />\n港人痛失科大高材生、<br />\n何君堯到底是否自編自導？<br />\n《政解．悶透社．王陽翎（于非）》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bXOsu5GUdjc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbXOsu5GUdjc&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=541bcf03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bXOsu5GUdjc</a><br />\n<br />\nPublished on Nov 8, 2019<br />\n<br />\n早前有指周梓樂進入停車場的原因，跟催淚彈無關，然而，最新的時序和證據顯示，周梓樂本來打算在11月4日零晨1:00離開停車場回家，卻在1:01分突然在天橋折返，再次進入停車場，隨後出事，到底真正原因是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n今晚不少港人紛紛前往綽念周梓樂之死，要當局徹查真相。至於重看何君堯事件，他到底有多大機會自編自導自演？<br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n<br />\n【墮樓科大生】警重組周梓樂墮樓前經過 離家後經天橋往返停車場<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/396051/墮樓科大生-...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F396051%2F%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F-...&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=7738768e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/396051/墮樓科大生-...</a><br />\n<br />\n目擊者指白車受阻延救援 警稱科大生墮樓後才入停車場 街坊指早已進入<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/artic...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Fartic...&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=ff65ec25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Fartic...&h=ae12aaf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/artic...</a>"},{"pid":"436e5b9d371802435c6d585e497fe50b1a518799","tid":1700762,"uid":249263,"like":